original_title: Duck Commander Presents: The Commander's Kitchen
overview: Come on in and have a seat as Phil and Kay Robertson, along with their family, share with you their favorite dishes.  Watch as they give step by step instructions on how to cook some of the best recipes Lousiana has to offer.  This is one mouth-watering treat you will not want to miss.
tagline: Hey! This is one mouth watering treat you will not want to miss.
title: Duck Commander Presents: The Commander's Kitchen
